{"tid":2511674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"5名中學生被捕 大埔金舖搶劫案","createTime":"2021-05-01T05:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T05:52:52.000Z","uid":62930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0683f3068a50769be4bfd8da67ee4f49340b746","tid":2511674,"uid":62930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"2021-05-01 12:02<br />\n<br />\n大埔前日(4月29日)發生劫案，當日下午4時許，2名男子假扮客人進入大埔廣場商場2樓一間金行，聲稱選購金飾。2人其後趁職員不覺時，擸走2條共值約5萬港元的金鏈後奪門而逃。警方到場調查後將案列作搶劫，交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，警方經深入調查及翻查閉路電視影片，成功鎖定目標人物，並於案發後12小時內迅速展開行動，拘捕5名男童(14至17歲)。據了解，被捕男童分別涉嫌在案中負責「睇水」及落手作案，警方將於稍後詳述案情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeAoeU2vUAmP762du1sfv8xr4jFvDESf5AYW5QfopXAS4?filename=9oMq5vs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9oMq5vs.png&h=bafc5624&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTPGFARYT74shn8ri9GUcm3RX6ypAgmNGLm9FmSCnnxZV?filename=QLYw03S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLYw03S.png&h=673d139a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWQ6h4Wws3PNWBizRGJLFLkPn8eaZCjwbvmPjFJGY2kXc?filename=s5LSLvz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5LSLvz.png&h=4ae1e519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5408856cb386cd61cf9f422ac91a1e3185aa09b9","tid":2511674,"uid":62930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"傻閪mk仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbfd00f2f14229a1f0039e10cc79e3181b63a39","tid":2511674,"u